### Variabel Konfigurasi Global
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check API
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 1. Register User Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@email.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

###

### 2. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@email.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

###

### 3. Get User Profile (Butuh AuthToken)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Ambal Semua Kuis
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Ambil Detail Kuis Berdasarkan ID (Misal ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Ambil Leaderboard Global
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Ambil Custom Materials (Misal Topik nodejs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/materials/nodejs
Accept: application/json
